	heroObjectPosition={`center center`}
	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you are a father, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You provide, protect, correct, show up at the games, carry the worry no one sees — and quietly wonder if you are getting it right. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on any phone — and it reveals God as <em>Father</em> from Genesis to Revelation. Whether you are searching for "Bible verses for fathers," "encouragement for dads," or healing for your own father-wound, it begins in one place: before you are a father, you are a beloved son of a perfect Father.`}
	keyTakeaway={`Every man fathers out of what he received. You cannot pour out a love you have not taken in — so before you father anyone, let yourself be fathered by God, and love your children from the overflow.`}
	painsHeading={`The weight fathers carry`}
	painsIntroHtml={`Most dads are trying hard and still feel they fall short. Many are fathering with a wound of their own — an absent, harsh, or distant father whose silence still echoes. And across a generation, the cost of father-absence has grown into one of the quietest crises in the country.`}
	painStats={[
