		{ ref: `Galatians 4:6`, slug: `galatians`, ch: 4, text: `Because you are sons, your Father has sent the Spirit of His Son into our hearts, crying, "Abba! Father!"`, note: `Sonship comes before fatherhood — the cry of "Abba" is meant to fill you before you fill your children.` },
