		{ ref: `Ephesians 3:14`, slug: `ephesians`, ch: 3, text: `For this reason I bow my knees before the Father, from whom every family in heaven and on earth is named.`, note: `Your fatherhood is not the origin — it is named after His. Go to the Source to learn the role.` },
