	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for fathers`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as the Father you needed`, bodyHtml: `Every other Bible names Him "God." The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals Him as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> onward. For a man with a father-wound, that changes everything: the God you read becomes the Dad you always longed for.` },
		{ heading: `It fills the tank you father from`, bodyHtml: `Free to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">read online</a> with audio on every chapter, it is built for a busy dad's real week — listen on the drive, read a few minutes before bed, and let the Father feed <em>you</em> before you pour into your kids.` },
