	voicesHeading={`What these fathers of the faith found in the Father`}
	voicesIntroHtml={`Some of the men God used most were shaped not by their own strength but by a deep trust in their Father in heaven. In their own words:`}
	voices={[
		{ quote: `God's work done in God's way will never lack God's supply.`, name: `Hudson Taylor`, role: `missionary who trusted his Father in heaven to provide for everything`, photo: `https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/42b6c06127e93dce38657c53f745bf42194152eb-283x400.jpg` },
		{ quote: `God is willing to take charge of the life that is wholly yielded to Him.`, name: `Andrew Murray`, role: `who taught a generation to abide in the Father's love`, photo: `https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/133bc45cfa954cf1ae99b7afac5954eca764ed70-500x830.jpg` },
		{ quote: `There is heaven in the depth of that word — Father.`, name: `Charles Spurgeon`, role: `the “Prince of Preachers”`, photo: `https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/e48a128da123135241be9c95cf35b37498d94ea5-500x617.jpg` },
